textBeforeTable: To locate the schools and their principals for your district, click on your districts' name on the list below. If a principal's name must be changed, fill out the Principal Exception Form for the Fall 2008 School Accountability Reports. The form may include multiple schools and must include the corrected principal data, and the name and signature of the person requesting the change and the date of the request. Fax the Principal Exception Form to Annette Severson at 303 866-6888 by Friday August 8th. Any Principal Exception Form received after that date will not be reflected in the Fall 2008 school accountabilty reports.
